{"an4.116:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 4.116 ","an4.116:0.2":"12. Kesivagga ","an4.116:0.3":"Appamadasutta ","an4.116:1.1":"“Catuhi, bhikkhave, thanehi appamado karaniyo. ","an4.116:1.2":"Katamehi catuhi? ","an4.116:1.3":"Kayaduccaritam, bhikkhave, pajahatha, kayasucaritam bhavetha; ","an4.116:1.4":"tattha ca ma pamadattha. ","an4.116:1.5":"Vaciduccaritam, bhikkhave, pajahatha, vacisucaritam bhavetha; ","an4.116:1.6":"tattha ca ma pamadattha. ","an4.116:1.7":"Manoduccaritam, bhikkhave, pajahatha, manosucaritam bhavetha; ","an4.116:1.8":"tattha ca ma pamadattha. ","an4.116:1.9":"Micchaditthim, bhikkhave, pajahatha, sammaditthim bhavetha; ","an4.116:1.10":"tattha ca ma pamadattha. ","an4.116:2.1":"Yato kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno kayaduccaritam pahinam hoti kayasucaritam bhavitam, vaciduccaritam pahinam hoti vacisucaritam bhavitam, manoduccaritam pahinam hoti manosucaritam bhavitam, micchaditthi pahina hoti sammaditthi bhavita, so na bhayati samparayikassa maranassa”ti. ","an4.116:2.2":"Chattham. "}